onal configuration of Windchill (or similar PLM platforms).\n* Contribute to the definition of data models, workflows, change management processes, and document structures.\n* Provide guidance on best practices, PLM governance, and system usage.\n* Support UAT, training sessions, and user enablement.\n\n*Project & Stakeholder Leadership*\n\n* Act as the primary functional point of contact for the customer.\n* Coordinate with technical and nearshore teams (Poland, Asia) ensuring smooth delivery.\n* Facilitate communication between business representatives, IT teams, and technical stakeholders.\n* Present PLM solutions and progress to management and executive audiences.\n* Contribute to project planning, estimation, and scope definition.\n\n*Required Qualifications:*\n\n*PLM & Technical Expertise*\n\n* 7+ years of experience with PLM systems (Windchill strongly preferred).\n* Strong understanding of PLM processes: BOM/BOP, workflows, configuration & change management, document management, ERP interaction.\n* Experience with system configuration and functional administration.\n* Exposure to customization and integration concepts (ERP, CAD, MES).\n* Experience in industries such as aerospace, automotive, pharma, or manufacturing is a plus.\n\n*Leadership & Communication*\n\n* Ability to lead workshops and guide functional decisions.\n* Experience working with distributed, multicultural teams.\n* Strong communication skills, able to articulate complex topics to both technical and business stakeholders.\n* Natural leadership qualities and proactive mindset.\n\n*Languages*\n\n* French & English required; Spanish is an advantage.\n\n*What We Offer*\n\n* Opportunity to work on a strategic, high-complexity PLM program.\n* Senior consulting role with strong influence on solution direction.\n* Collaboration with international teams across Europe & Asia.\n* Growth opportunities in a dynamic, innovation-driven environment.\n* A chance to shape PLM solutions for major enterprise customers.\n\nType d'emploi : Temps plein, CDI\n\nRémunération : 55 000,00€ par an\n\nAvantages :\n* Formation linguistique offerte\n* Prise en charge du transport quotidien\n\n\n\nExpérience:\n* Product Lifecycle Management: 5 ans (Requis)\n* PTC Windchill : 5 ans (Requis)\n\nLangue:\n* Français (Requis)\n* Anglais (Requis)\n\nDisposition à l'égard des déplacements professionnels:\n* 50 % (Requis)\n\nLieu du poste : Télétravail"}
