{"source":"linkedin","source_id":"4379595710","title":"Sales Executive (Outbound Sales)","company":"Altery","location":"London","remote":false,"salary":"","posted_at":"","url":"https://newfts.bamboohr.com/careers/164?source=LinkedIn","description":"About UsAre you passionate about FinTech and ready to make a tangible impact in a dynamic company where your decisions shape the future? Altery could be the next chapter in your professional journey!We’re expanding rapidly and looking for an experienced  Sales Executive to help grow our international client base. In this role, you’ll lead high-impact sales initiatives that drive revenue growth and strengthen our presence in global markets. You’ll own the entire sales cycle – from strategising and prospecting to negotiating and closing complex B2B deals across diverse industries. To succeed in this role, you will need 7+ years of experience in fast-paced B2B sales or business development, with at least 2–3 years focused on selling financial services and payments products.This is a remote role, but you’ll need to be based in the EMEA region.What you’ll be doingDrive outbound sales into new regions and market segments using your own networks and executing global targeted outreach strategies in line with Altery’s go-to-market plan.Own the end-to-end business development &amp; sales cycle – from prospecting and pitching to negotiating and closing – using a mix of outreach channels including cold calls, networking, email, social media, and industry events.Manage the entire outbound sales process from first contact to close, with a focus on B2B international companies and entrepreneurs.Build and maintain a strong sales pipeline, converting high-potential prospects into active Altery customers.Collaborate with the Customer Success team to ensure continued engagement and long-term growth of the customers you bring on board.Identify and develop relationships with strategic partners across various industries.Keep detailed records of