cross all settings.Why should you apply?This is a fantastic opportunity to work in a growing FinTech environment with excellent career progression available.With a global client base the role offers an opportunity to experience a wide variety of digital transformation projects – each with their own unique requirements and opportunities.We take career progression seriously, with investment into the WDX Academy for new and existing employee learning and development.You will learn a lot with exposure to multiple complex client needs.Who is best suited to this role?Industry Knowledge: Comprehensive knowledge of private banking and wealth management. Wider knowledge of asset management, corporate banking and retail banking is advantages.Sales or Consultancy Experience: Prior experience in pre-sales, consultancy or sales roles is expected.Commercial Awareness: Strong understanding of market dynamics and commercial strategies, particularly in the private banking and wealth management sectors.Technical Acumen: Semi-technical understanding of banking system architectures, including cloud vs. on-premise solutions, multi-tenancy, and data models. Coding skills are not required.Independent &amp; Team Working Ability: Capable of working both as part of a team and independently, managing multiple responsibilities and adapting to changing priorities.Quick Learner: Demonstrated ability to absorb new information and methodologies swiftly, adapting to evolving business needs.Presentation Skills: Confident, clear, concise communicator with the ability to present proposals and conduct demos effectively to C-level representatives. Ability to read the room and to confidently improvise, where required.Pre-Sales Process Understanding: Solid grasp of the typical pre-sales process, enabling effective engagement with clients.Attention to Detail: Exceptional attention to detail in presentation materials and outputs, ensuring high-quality, accurate deliverables.Relationship Management: Proven ability to establish and maintain strong relationships with clients at all levels, both internally and externally.We believe we offer career defining opportunities and are on a journey that will build awesome memories in a diverse and inclusive culture. If you are looking for more than just a job, get in touch."}
