hampion\nKeeps track of new requests coming from customers and would want to influence product management\nInfluences product features to fix common problems\nIs aware of limited time from engineers and wants to learn everything or use all tools at disposal (google search, tech docs etc.) before engaging with the engineering team\n\nWhat you’ll need (Basic Qualifications)\n\nHands-on 5+ years of Professional Services experience implementing HSM or Key Management platforms and use cases.\nBe in any discipline or equivalent\nFlexible working in different time zones depending on the customer\nExperience in designing, demonstrating, and executing proof-of-concepts (PoCs) for customers independently.\nStrong technical proficiency is required, with hands-on experience in systems administration, container technologies, and scripting languages.\nDemonstrated hands-on experience with at least one HSM or KMS platform, including but not limited to AWS CloudHSM, AWS KMS, Google Cloud KMS, Azure Key Vault, or IBM Key Protect.\nStrong working knowledge of cryptographic interfaces, such as PKCS#11, CAPI, CNG, JCE, and KMIP.\nExperienced with various database encryption, tokenization, certificate management other key management operations.\nAbility to work in a highly fast-paced, rapid growth environment.\nStrong collaboration, written and communication skills\n***Must live in the UAE***\n\nBenefits\n\nWe offer a collaborative work environment, amazing equity, great benefits, competitive salary, and the opportunity to redefine data security in for hybrid cloud, AI and Post Quantum.\nQuarterly recharge days\n40 hours of Volunteer Time Off/year\nInternet stipend\nFriendly culture that brings the best out of everybody\nBeing able to work Fully remote\n\nFortanix is an equal opportunity employer that celebrates diversity and is committed to creating an inclusive workplace with equal opportunity for all applicants and teammates. Our goal is to recruit the most talented people from a diverse candidate pool regardless of race, colour, religion, age, gender, gender identity, sexual orientation or any other status. If you’re interested in working in a fast growing, exciting working environment – we encourage you to apply!"}
