ting this application, I certify that all information provided herein is true, accurate, and complete to the best of my knowledge. I understand that any false or misleading information may result in disqualification from consideration or, if discovered after acceptance, may lead to immediate dismissal.Orange Logic is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all our employees.We respect your privacy. Learn more about how we handle applicant data in our Global Career Privacy Notice."}
